il 2019 causing great inconvenience. The petitioners therefore request that the House of Commons to urge the Government and BDUK to facilitate immediate connection of superfast broadband. And the petitioners remain, etc. [P002065]     Share                   ×   Suggest Correction            Your Details:         Enter your suggested correction:   0 /1000          Please prove you are not a robot.        Close  Submit               A-Z index | Glossary | Contact us | Freedom of Information | Data Protection |  Jobs | Using this website |  Copyright     © Parliamentary Copyright                     Cookies: We use cookies to give you the best possible experience on our site. By continuing to use the site you
